OL,5, Bernie Ecclestone, the former boss of  
OL,6, Formula One, has admitted fraud after  
OL,7, failing to declare more than #400m held
OL,8, in a trust in Singapore.               
OL,10,FThe 92-year-old billionaire did not    
OL,11,Fdisclose the trust when asked by tax   
OL,12,Fauthorities if he had wealth overseas. 
OL,14,FEcclestone has agreed in a civil       
OL,15,Fsettlement to repay almost #653m to HM 
OL,16,FRevenues and Customs, the court heard. 
OL,18,FHe had originally been due to stand    
OL,19,Ftrial next month after initially       
OL,20,Fpleading not guilty.                   
